Package com.complexible.stardog.api.impl

Class Summary
AbstractConnection Abstract base class for stardog connection implementations.
AbstractQuery<T> Base implementation of the Query interface which provides implementations for all the setParameter methods for the parameterized query.
AbstractReadQuery<T>
AdderImpl Default implementation of Adder a helper class for a Connection which provides the functionality to add RDF data to a Connection.
DatabaseNamespaces Implementation of namespaces interface that uses database metadata for storing the namespaces.
DelegatingConnection Connection implementation for use in implementing Connection decorators
GetterImpl Default implementation of the Getter interface.
PooledConnection Connection decorator which adds support for connection objects being used in a pool.
RemoverImpl Default implementation of the Remover interface.
 

Enum Summary
ConnectionChangeType The type of a Change to a Connection.
